                    </div>
                    <span>As we move out of the earlier client/server and the web enabled environment, developing a clear enterprise architecture design will be crucial for organizations that wish to manage costs and deliver value. Service-Orientated Architecture is a great field manual for executives that need to deliver mission critical system that can provide the ability to refresh technology without major impact to the entire environment. This should be on every architect's bookshelf.</span>
                  
              
